Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:11.80,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy being a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:17.14,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm a monster, no matter how many times that golem punched me, I didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:22.64,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm a monster, I'm able to stand up to that golem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:27.06,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I will use my power to protect those I cherish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.66,0:00:32.03,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm fortunate... to be a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:33.12,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.12,0:00:34.66,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'll let it end this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:35.49,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kazaki-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:38.98,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kazakiri!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.98,0:00:42.56,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'll let it end... in such a stupid way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:48.67,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,500)\pos(118,498)}#24 Imaginary Number Sector\NFive Elements Institution
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.86,0:01:07.44,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for Ellis, I had her go ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.64,0:01:11.15,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,I should think she's reached her target by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.23,0:01:16.11,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps... the target might already have been shredded to chunks of meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:18.49,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You piece of...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:20.88,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.88,0:01:23.37,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,You just stay here and be my opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.37,0:01:25.09,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately that girl got by.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.09,0:01:26.21,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kazakiri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.07,0:01:29.79,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared you were able to destroy Ellis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.79,0:01:31.63,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,I want war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.81,0:01:34.97,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:39.39,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a balance between\Nmagic and science, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:40.63,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:46.00,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,When espers use magic, their body will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:47.69,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard of that at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:49.40,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:52.07,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you think that was weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:54.52,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,How would anyone know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:59.49,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Because someone tried to, around twenty years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:02.60,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,back when there was a movement to have magic and science walk together,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:04.74,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,which was started by one of our inner factions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:09.72,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,They were trying to give birth to a new type of caster that possessed both esper abilities and magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:12.59,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,The result was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.18,0:02:16.77,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Ellis was my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:23.43,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Ellis was one of the espers brought in by the faction in Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:27.69,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the spells I taught her,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:29.37,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Ellis ended up spilling all her blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.32,0:02:35.10,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,To save me from the Knights that came to destroy our facility,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:38.01,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Ellis was beaten to death by their maces.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:41.70,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot co-exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:43.79,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Magicians in the world of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.79,0:02:45.59,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Scientists in the world of science!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:51.33,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't know the boundaries of our own fields properly, the same mistakes will be repeated over and over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:54.62,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, this is not making any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:57.84,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If this is about protecting each other,\Nwhat the hell is starting a war going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:03:01.64,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you're not actually going to start one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:09.09,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to accomplish what you want,\Nyou just want a situation where they're about to go to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:12.56,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me so highly, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:15.03,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you look at me with pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:19.20,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,The clay is my ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:23.07,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,And in this abyss surrounded by clay, I am the ruler!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:26.75,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... she's going to destroy the entire tunnel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:28.20,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Everything, crumble down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:29.66,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Like a puppet of mud!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:31.23,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, what should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.67,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Touma, did you know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:37.82,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The direction and standing position of the caster in the formula used...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:40.71,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Get it wrong just by a little, and it won't function at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:42.91,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know that golden ratio, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:43.97,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:45.43,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Devour the foolish ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:47.39,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Melt them into the mud!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:51.35,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The magic seals on the walls and ceiling are used to bury me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:54.31,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,And I will recompose your body with all this mud!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:58.74,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then, she didn't need to have seals on the ground, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:03.66,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That must mean these seals are the ones that protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:05.08,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:09.50,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:25.09,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:27.30,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:34.60,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,I need to... create war... the reason for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:38.60,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Academy City is letting down its guard too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:45.38,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Church is letting an outsider have possession of Index Librorum Prohibitorum, showing their naivety.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:48.97,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same situation that occurred during Ellis' time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:52.12,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,A tragedy of that scale took place back then when there were just small factions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:57.48,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,If Academy City and the English Purist Church in their entireties are joining hands-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:58.66,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This is pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:02.97,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and be angry. Be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:06.32,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But, what the hell did Kazakiri do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:08.56,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What did Index do to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:10.97,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You point your weapon at someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.76,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...and that's when real wars happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:16.11,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:17.58,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:21.00,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,I want to slaughter all magicians and espers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.56,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:27.96,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't want magicians and espers fighting each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:33.20,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,My mind was in conflict from the very beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:38.43,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,I have more than one conviction...\NI have as many as the number of stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:41.70,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:46.25,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...that there was only one thing\Nyou believed in from the very beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:52.43,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you just didn't want to lose your dear friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:58.83,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,In your eyes, did Index look like she didn't want to be with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:04.19,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Did we look like we were going to fight unless we were isolated in our own separate worlds?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:08.52,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,We are able to live together without doing such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:11.95,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So don't take my dear friend away from me either!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:15.04,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Intimus115!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:21.92,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:24.88,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,When she said she has as many convictions as the number of stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:27.51,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Die, esper!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:29.18,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You understood the one emotion inside you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:33.68,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...of wanting someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.24,0:06:40.19,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...to stop you, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:51.15,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,This may be bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:53.83,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Long distance manipulation has been switched to automaton mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:54.95,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I can't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:56.90,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Ellis...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:07:00.91,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,I can't reach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:03.92,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Ellis...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:08.84,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kazakiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:09.88,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Index!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:16.51,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:36.74,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.09,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyou... ka...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.49,0:07:46.50,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:48.62,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:50.88,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,It's still dangerous here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:14.18,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The golem went berserk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.74,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,It might be losing control of its regeneration ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:24.58,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka, let's run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.90,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,You hurry and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.02,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.83,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Hyouka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:32.59,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I need to stop that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:33.87,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:37.24,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,You can't think that you can fight a monster like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:40.25,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, you'll die for sure, Hyouka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:42.82,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:46.06,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not human either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:50.19,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... for not telling you all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:53.32,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:16.93,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,The ones to fight monsters... must also be monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:19.97,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go back there anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:23.17,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,That "time" will never happen again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:27.98,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.51,0:09:31.28,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I can't abandon her!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:33.24,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:37.41,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Because... she's my friend!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.92,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kazakiri!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:44.00,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:46.44,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:50.69,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...that there's still hope in the world you reside in...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.30,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...and that I'd show you that!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:05.39,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:10.86,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,...and so is the nice illusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:30.88,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's so messy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:33.82,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:37.98,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me this is your doing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:41.04,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,You know, while this does happen all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:43.71,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,how much trouble do you have to get yourself into?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:57.93,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:01.11,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,My, Oneesama!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:02.32,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,There you are-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.80,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... Oneesama, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:10.63,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:15.45,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,In the very near future,\NJudgment and Anti-Skill will come after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:18.05,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,Before this gets bad, let's run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:19.85,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I said this wasn't-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:45.83,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I knew from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:48.90,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone knew, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:54.53,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,When a monster reveals its true nature, they know what happens next.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.37,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:01.32,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,But what could I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:03.26,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,A friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:07.09,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,A person who called me a friend for the first time in my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:08.83,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to save her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:16.65,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Why must I lose this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:21.97,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Why must I be afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:25.55,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:32.46,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't want my dear friend to get hurt!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:35.42,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I stood up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:39.00,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be with her forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:42.10,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that I could be good friends with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:46.44,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,But... it was impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.13,0:12:49.86,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,...even if she became scared of me... hated me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:53.45,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,...I couldn't watch her get killed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.19,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:02.18,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:10.12,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, then you're not a monster, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:19.38,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I know this sounds corny, but you're human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:21.09,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:23.62,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:26.99,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Your illusion isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:34.35,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:41.88,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:44.41,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:51.64,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... not human...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:14:00.15,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,...yet why is she looking at me... as a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:06.21,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, maybe your composition is a bit different from a human's,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:09.57,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,and you might be able to do things other people can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.43,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:22.30,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But, it doesn't change the fact that you're Index's friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.74,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,You happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:34.46,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're another step closer to the completion of a key...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:36.10,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,...that can control the Imaginary Number Sector - Five Elements Institution.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:40.00,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, you're a monster to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:45.84,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,To think that the Imaginary Number Sector's true nature is the AIM dispersion field itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:47.60,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure no one would think of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:52.66,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Then, to be adding self-consciousness to and helping the materialization of something like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:54.49,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you to be sane at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:57.51,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking, Aleister?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:14:59.74,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:06.09,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,The Imaginary Number Sector is a kind of aggregation of power that exists in a separate dimension from humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:09.21,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,An organism born from that aggregation is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:13.51,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,I know what that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:16.01,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,An angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:22.00,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,If the inhabitants of the Imaginary Number Sector,\Nlike Kazakiri, were "Angels" per se,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:25.87,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,then the city in which they live in would be... in other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:30.90,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're trying to artificially create Heaven?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:36.16,Default,Crowley,0000,0000,0000,,Throwing words like "Angels" and "Heaven" at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:37.90,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Cut me some slack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:40.02,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,As if there'd be someone who'd know more than you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:43.98,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Aleister Crowley, the magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:50.30,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,From this time's incident,\Nthe world has slowly begun to tremble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.75,0:15:55.69,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,You purposely lured in a member of the English Purist Church and defeated her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:02.19,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,What you're thinking is completely beyond me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:06.69,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're going to take advantage of that Imagine Breaker, then be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:13.26,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Face him with half-assed beliefs,\Nand his right hand will eat your illusions alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:21.99,Default,Crowley,0000,0000,0000,,The illusions I believed in... were destroyed a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.43,0:16:27.34,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:29.93,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'm completely unscratched!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:31.78,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I'm good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:34.04,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This is a sign that I'm learning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:34.99,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:37.33,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijyo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:43.81,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,You really, really, really LOVE causing trouble for others, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:48.13,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, for you to be in Anti-Skill's custody...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:54.04,Default,Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you to be careful of Kazakiri Hyouka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:17:02.01,Default,Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,Your personality of going all out when it comes to women needs a good amount of tweaking sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:07.10,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, these two people in the back scare me,\Nso could I stay in the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:09.65,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,In absolute-rest, no-visitor conditions-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:13.90,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:15.24,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Your skirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:17.58,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:20.11,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:22.65,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:24.94,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I really think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:27.76,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,It was already weird to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:30.15,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,It might be even weirder now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:31.55,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:37.57,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka, you-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:39.65,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:44.31,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,My body is like a lump of esper power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:51.41,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I do, it'll never change the fact that I'm an unstable entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:54.27,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Is this because of Touma's right hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:55.27,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:18:01.95,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,If his powers really affected me,\Nthen I would've been gone already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:05.48,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:11.41,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,About his power, I don't know too much about it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:15.46,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Esper abilities, alone, aren't enough to explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:19.94,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:22.12,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:28.19,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.85,0:18:32.03,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:42.06,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry, I'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:46.16,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,My body is formed from the powers of many, many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:51.86,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I did disappear, it wouldn't mean I'd died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:54.62,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,It'd just mean you wouldn't be able to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:58.02,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't tell,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:19:01.52,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I will always be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:05.42,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:12.04,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,We'll hang out together again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:14.05,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:27.08,Default,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, second semester is very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:29.96,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,But I have so much time, I'm bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:33.42,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma wouldn't pay attention to me or play with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:38.63,Default,blue,0000,0000,0000,,Look, this is what magicians should look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:40.01,Default,blue,0000,0000,0000,,Moe, right? Moe, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.79,Default,blue,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Hime-yan, you do it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:44.68,Default,Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... moe then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:48.85,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, boys and girls, we're going to start homeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:51.79,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:53.65,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Tsuchimikado-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:20:00.09,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I started my job already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:13.39,Default,Yomi,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of those two, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:15.08,Default,Yoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:28.14,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:29.56,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,My ribbon has drifted into...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:32.48,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,...Oneesama's forbidden sanctuary!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:33.91,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,KUROKO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:53.96,Default,Laura,0000,0000,0000,,A situation has arisen where we need\Nthe Index Librorum Prohibitorum's assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:57.37,Default,Laura,0000,0000,0000,,Have her keeper come, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.37,0:20:59.34,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,"Keeper", eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:01.08,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:03.01,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki and I will leave for Japan right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:06.97,Default,Laura,0000,0000,0000,,The problem, however, is we cannot contact Kanzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:10.41,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Archbishop?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:14.27,Default,Laura,0000,0000,0000,,I am wearing a rather dull attire for a change,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:16.65,Default,Laura,0000,0000,0000,,you shan't address me by my formal title.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:19.45,Default,Laura,0000,0000,0000,,Laura Stuart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:21.73,Default,Laura,0000,0000,0000,,You shall address me by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:27.09,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Daihasei Festival - the strongest in Academy City
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:35.29,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Index-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.42,0:21:40.98,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, you forgot the fridge was empty, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:45.95,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, eating something delicious all by yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:49.43,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, this is leftover from lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:52.66,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, you're the only one who even had a lunch, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:58.36,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry, I'm hungry, I'm hungry!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:03.67,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Such misfortune!!!
