Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.50,0:19:41.18,ED2R,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Yuzurenai omoi dake wa mune ni himeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:49.78,ED2R,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Guuzen to warau koe kakiwake
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:58.63,ED2R,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Tadoritsu mukou gawa jibun wo shinjiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:07.90,ED2R,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Omoidasareru koto wa kanaetai negai wa itsumo
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.45,0:20:15.56,ED2R,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Mou ichido mou ichido dake to idomitsuzuketeta
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.65,0:20:17.42,ED2R,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be3\3c&H030487&}Sukoshi dake
Dialogue: 3,0:20:17.14,0:20:25.03,ED2R,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Nakushita omoi wa sou katachi wo kaetetemo kitto
Dialogue: 4,0:20:24.65,0:20:36.57,ED2R,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Torimodosu sono hi ga kuru made sagashi tsuzuketeku
Dialogue: 4,0:20:31.89,0:20:38.46,ED2R,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be3\3c&H030487&}Sukoshi dake mou ichido
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:34.78,ED2E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Neither the nonchalant present, nor the unforseeable future
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.50,0:19:41.18,ED2E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Know of the firm resolve within my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:49.78,ED2E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Fighting my way past the coincidental laughs,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:58.63,ED2E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}And arriving on the other side, believing in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:07.90,ED2E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}They are always remembered, the wishes I want granted,
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.45,0:20:15.56,ED2E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}One more time, one more time, as I kept challenging.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.65,0:20:17.42,ED2E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be3\3c&H030487&}Just a bit more
Dialogue: 3,0:20:17.14,0:20:25.03,ED2E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}The memories that were lost, I will get them back,
Dialogue: 4,0:20:24.65,0:20:36.57,ED2E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Even if they change, until the day comes, I will keep searching.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:31.89,0:20:38.46,ED2E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be3\3c&H030487&}Just a bit more, one more time.
